{"tid":1698372,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：陳百祥KO杜汶澤：有理不在聲高！暴力應該停止！","createTime":"2019-11-07T12:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:44:03.000Z","uid":65371,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b936c576e7a7802870ee64bf49f539cbdcc348d3","tid":1698372,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/988387914869350/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393304404377707%2Fposts%2F988387914869350%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=6afd68e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/988387914869350/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【陳百祥KO杜汶澤：有理不在聲高！暴力應該停止！】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYjVtDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYjVtDb.jpg&h=5cfa3512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，知名藝人陳百祥和港星杜汶澤參加香港電台節目《視點31》，就近期香港形勢進行辯論。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">陳百祥一如既往地以理撐警，多次提醒杜汶澤「不是聲音大就代表正確」</span></span>，強調「暴力應該停止」！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">陳百祥的淡定自若和理性言論在香港和內地均得到眾多網友支持。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n陳百祥表示，這5個月對香港來說是悲劇，坦言自己從未見過這麼亂的香港。<br />\n<br />\n針對杜汶澤指責警察「濫暴」，陳百祥指出，警察負責香港的法治，法治是香港的基石，如果沒有法治，香港就會『淪陷』。人們能從直播畫面裡看到暴力是從哪邊開始的，如果不是年輕人投擲汽油彈、拿攻擊性武器攻擊警察，警察不會反擊。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">他還以美國警察為例，指出香港警察不是濫暴，而是過分克制。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於杜汶澤所說的民調，陳百祥表示，這樣的民調、戴耀廷等人寫的東西沒有可信度。<br />\n<br />\n被問及藝人是否因為政見而喪失在內地發展機會，陳百祥表示，自己只看到女藝人馬蹄露因政見不同被人「私了」。<br />\n<br />\n辯論40分鐘後，陳百祥總結道，香港是我們的家，不想看到香港亂，暴力應該停止。希望大家可以像他和杜汶澤一樣，坐下來溝通，不管如何爭論都不要動手動腳，這才是基本的民主精神。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ho1dPb-rXlI7Zd0u9_oz9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fho1dPb-rXlI7Zd0u9_oz9A&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=032b20ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ho1dPb-rXlI7Zd0u9_oz9A</a><br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n歡迎關注公署官方微信公眾號(帳號:fmcoprc)，希望為你提供豐富有益的資訊和便捷周到的服務。"},{"pid":"ae5977f5582a5801666f23181d1d2114bbdc3a47","tid":1698372,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"321cbae37127c8c4ab3b0a8e2d3535001b46651d","tid":1698372,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e9c84d43bf8b2d922dac617ccd52f9a1473ae6","tid":1698372,"uid":146285,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"係人民日報唔係口交部WO"},{"pid":"ca341c0e2b579846842735572d7ee9222849da2c","tid":1698372,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"支那外交部都幾撚得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ff76e085ec752aa8feac729e50fa67cc77ffb6","tid":1698372,"uid":24104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:23:20.000Z","msg":"贏在面皮厚"},{"pid":"f14909cdbed6ceff1524f34cc3ae14a89d959647","tid":1698372,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"小丑都上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004a2b1f40d6bfe2555db03ca3949d6640e900d1","tid":1698372,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14909cdbed6ceff1524f34cc3ae14a89d959647","tid":1698372,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"小丑都上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"贏咗場辯論，點都打番個飛機先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605e459241895337eedbd89925eeeba8fe377818","tid":1698372,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislik